| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4444 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6e0d4f0e-f149-5c1d-a199-3b9c54b5db7f"
